Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
deleteAllInstGroups(25.10)                          deleteAllInstGroups(25.10)

Name
       deleteAllInstGroups - Removes all instance groups

Syntax
       deleteAllInstGroups

       [-help]

       Removes  all instance groups. Instance groups are user-created and con-
       tain instances and/or other groups. Use this  command  after  importing
       the design.

Parameters
       -help  Outputs a brief description of the deleteAllInstGroups command.

              For a detailed description of the command, use the man command:

              man deleteAllInstGroups

Examples
              * The following command removes all instance groups:

                deleteAllInstGroups

